{
  "stem": "10162.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 60.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His last name was Asztalos-- Sandor Asztalos, A-S-Z-T-A-L-O-S.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a writer, a poet, a musicologist, a true, true genius.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He really was a genius.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he just was too much of a genius for his own good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He just didn't have the character to carry this incredible package up there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was nine years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yet he was a professor at the Debrecen University at-- at-- comparative literature.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was the cultural commissar in Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And right after we married, we went to Budapest, where he became the head of everything that had to do with the culture in the ministry, you know, with theater and opera and ballet and everything.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was writing at the same time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, he wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was one thing about my generation-- after the war, we were-- I don't know, what we would call-- the lost-- some kind of a lost generation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the way the kids who came back, you know, who-- many of us never came back, many of our best friends.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not just our friends didn't come back, but their parents or grandparents or aunts or uncles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nobody in this world-- I'm here to talk about my family, but there's no one to talk about their family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Entire families vanished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we would meet, you know, boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say, well, what are you doing tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'll say or he'll say, oh, I think I'm going to Argentina.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you want to come, we are meeting at 6 o'clock on [NON-ENGLISH] on the-- don't know what-- in this place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you want to come?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll go first to Italy and then by boat to Argentina.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I would say, oh, maybe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That sounds great.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I probably wanted to go, but I overslept or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is the way we went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it didn't matter who was Jewish and who was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just didn't want to hear about war and differences and hostilities or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had-- my son was born in '52 and my daughter in '53.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, his Hungarian name was Gabor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he changed his name in France Gabriele and then in America to Garry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My daughter was Anna in Hungarian and became Anne in France and in America.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a very, very, very difficult, turbulent marriage, because he was a very self-destructive and tortured genius.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to it-- to all this greatly added that this was the birthplace of Stalinism in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So here is this incredible talent, writing fantastic poetry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they keep telling him-- and novels-- and they keep telling him that this is-- this is expressionist, and that's surrealist, and that is-- you know, I mean, those were labels that were-- that they were tantamount to say that you should-- you should go to jail or go to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, this was an anti-class action.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to somebody, to a creative person, to say all the time, well, take this name out, and you have to put in there something about Tito, you know, that he is the enchained dog of imperialists or something like that, it really, really drove him crazy, even crazier.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was an alcoholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was just a horrendous thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- How are you taking all of this after all you went through?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- it was-- it was like a continuation of the whole thing, plus that I admired him very much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw him suffer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was just-- and I was-- he was from the right background besides.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was like a self-made man because of who he was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he came from a very modest background.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was the capitalist background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I didn't dare to open my mouth anyway, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I was a class alien.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody was scared in those-- in those days in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were the worst, worst days of Stalinism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We who went through the days of-- the years of Nazism, we knew that no matter how bad it is, it's not as bad as that was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it even hardened our differences.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was-- it was horrendous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just the fear and the-- the lying, the-- that was the worst part.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the worst part, that you had to lie to your own child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you didn't dare to-- you were afraid you would speak in your dream.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because actually the expression that the walls have ears were true.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
